ESCAPE.original: All for One
Game Type
~r~The getaway boat is on land, it needs to get back into water.
ESCAPE.translated: ~r~逃亡用的船被搞到陆地上了，它需要回到水里。

ESCAPE.original: Rounds
Head to the ~b~getaway vehicle.
The ~COL_NET_2~cops~s~ have been alerted. Get to the ~b~getaway vehicle.
ESCAPE.translated: ~COL_NET_2~条子~s~已接到警报。前往~b~逃亡车辆。

ESCAPE.original: GAME IS ABOUT TO END
You are the team's Boss.
A crook has got into the getaway vehicle.
ESCAPE.translated: 一名盗贼已经进入了逃亡载具。

ESCAPE.original: The ~COL_NET_1~crooks~s~ have been spotted, they are highly dangerous. Take them down.
ESCAPE.translated: ~COL_NET_1~盗贼们~s~已经被发现，他们极度危险。干掉他们。

ESCAPE.original: The boss needs to stay in the vehicle - the game will end shortly if he doesn't.
ESCAPE.translated: 团队老大需要待在载具里-如果他不的话游戏很快会结束。

ESCAPE.original: WAITING FOR VIP TO BE SELECTED.
A Crook needs to stay in the vehicle - the game will end shortly.
ESCAPE.translated: 盗贼需要待在车里-游戏将很快结束。

ESCAPE.original: Some of the crooks have got into the getaway vehicle.
ESCAPE.translated: 一些盗贼已经进入了逃亡载具。

ESCAPE.original: The Boss has reached the getaway vehicle.
ESCAPE.translated: 团队老大已经抵达了逃亡载具。

ESCAPE.original: The Boss has been taken out.
~r~The getaway vehicle has been destroyed. The round will end shortly.
ESCAPE.translated: ~r~逃亡载具已被摧毁。本回合即将结束。

ESCAPE.original: LEAVE
You are the boss, make your way to the ~b~getaway vehicle.
ESCAPE.translated: 你是团队老大，赶快前往~b~逃亡载具。

ESCAPE.original: Protect the ~COL_NET_1~Boss.
~r~The getaway vehicle has been flipped. The round will end shortly.
ESCAPE.translated: ~r~逃亡载具翻了。本回合即将结束。

ESCAPE.original: Find the ~COL_NET_1~Boss~s~ and take him out.
One for All
